high_descs: Turn around and then go to the left. Go to the left hand side of the bath tub.
Pick up the soap dispenser from the edge of the bath tub.
Turn around and turn left. Go to the sinks. Turn left again to face the toilet.
Place the soap dispenser on the back end of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move the soap dispenser to the back end of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and step forward, then turn left to approach the tub.
Pick up the right most bottle of soap on the counter attached to the tub.
Turn around and move forward, then go to the toilet on your left.
Put the bottle of soap on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a bottle of soap on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Pick up right pump dispenser from side of tub.
Turn around, proceed to wall.  Turn left and proceed to left sink.  Turn left to face toilet.
Put pump dispenser on back of toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move one pump dispenser from side of tub to back of toilet.
